{"tid":1363125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.27上街 反送中最前線 白髮婆婆揮舞巨幅英國旗","createTime":"2019-07-25T05:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T06:04:21.000Z","uid":50457,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8bbb7366758d523f93db9b22361940895333a1d6","tid":1363125,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"香港反送中運動期間，經常可在抗爭場合看見戴著眼鏡、六十三歲的「白髮婆婆」王鳳瑤（Alexandra Wong）；她揮舞著一面巨大的英國國旗，在警察和年輕人對峙時，站在最前線，一邊苦勸警方「香港人不打自己人」，一邊大聲提醒抗爭者要小心。<br />\n<br />\n王鳳瑤在年齡層普遍較低的「反送中」示威群眾中，相當顯眼。她說，揮舞英國國旗是因為懷念英國殖民時期的香港，「英國殖民時期對我們很好，我看到未來」；香港在主權移交中國後，狀況大不如前，失去很多寶貴的東西，「我站出來是為了香港的未來。我為香港的年輕人感到擔憂」。<br />\n<br />\n王鳳瑤出生香港深水埗，因為買不起房子，十三年前遷居中國深圳。為了到香港參加示威，<span style=\"color: red;\">王鳳瑤有時必須花上五小時的交通時間往返，回深圳時還必須換下寫有反政府標語的衣物，以免被盯上</span>，「在深圳的商家只敢擺出中國國旗，你必須私下偷偷問，才能買到我手中的英國國旗」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1300722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1300722&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUakErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=81fe6852\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1300722&h=ccc62b7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1300722</a><br />\n<br />\n連登仔，出動吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad9a1a947f8ad99f59fb11fe7a0fc54c5aeb7ab","tid":1363125,"uid":164920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:33:27.000Z","msg":"仲有英文名alexandra咁霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe14919642422b153c5c30322f9c83ebb90d334","tid":1363125,"uid":39174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"英國旗婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb10664fae1dc61630e62caeb8e86a5f296cfa6","tid":1363125,"uid":30635,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"王婆婆原來住深圳 咁樣仲覺得佢癲<br />\n個日屯門遊行2點已經見到佢<br />\n夜晚9點幾我去鄔小姐個追思會又見到佢<br />\n佢仲要夜媽媽返深圳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d87300c52310a5c9008329b22d691f9aeacf17d","tid":1363125,"uid":2110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"原來佢一直都玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70050df513067e68b6c5fe7768d0d33bc8d2365","tid":1363125,"uid":261043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />婆婆住深圳"},{"pid":"843e47965ac8e69e22f4a20adc6ef9adcf5091da","tid":1363125,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e70050df513067e68b6c5fe7768d0d33bc8d2365","tid":1363125,"uid":261043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />婆婆住深圳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:02:02.000Z","msg":"好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39c4daa4d9fa7dab67c7d5a77573db10d08b106","tid":1363125,"uid":192722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />報左出黎會唔會好危險<br />\n原來住深圳"}]}